\name{gosdt-package}
\alias{gosdt-package}
\alias{gosdt}
\title{R-native bindings to the GOSDT C++ solver}
\description{
Experimental interface to the General Optimal Sparse Decision Tree (GOSDT)
implementation shipped in the parent repository's \verb{src/libgosdt}
directory. This package is built without Python.

See \code{README.md} in this package directory for system requirements and
installation from source.
}
